nodes.text: A diner existed in the galaxy. When he did construction work in the Core Worlds, Ganzer visited the diner. There, he witnessed a Jedi Knight encounter two hustlers who had been winning meals off patrons.

The diner was first mentioned in John Jackson Miller's short story "The Ride" in the 2017 novella collection Canto Bight, released as part of the Journey to Star Wars: The Last Jedi multimedia project.
